## BaseTechniqueParams.renderOrder property

The render order of the objects created using this technique.

If not specified in style file, \[\[StyleSetEvaluator\]\] will assign monotonically increasing values according to style position in file.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
renderOrder?: DynamicProperty<number>;
```
